  "text": "Ribosomal proteins from strain AM1 grown on methanol medium were purified following the method reported previously [CITATION_1] . The MS spectra of ribosomal proteins were compared with the aforementioned WC-MS profile to identify the detected protein peaks based on the genome information of the strain.",
